title: Unlimited Health
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Raw, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, European
description: Amsterdam raw food cafe, juice bar, and takeaway - part of a yoga centre. Limited all raw vegan meals served in plastic pre-prepared containers. Honey and bee pollen used in some smoothies. Sells raw food specialty items, organic body care products, herbal supplements, and yoga lessons. Has online store.
